Package: rnim
Type: Package
Title: Simple package that allows you to load a library written in Nim
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Luis Castro-de-Araujo
Maintainer: Luis Castro-de-Araujo <ldearaujo@unimelb.edu.au>
Description: Very simple! You can write your memory and processing demanding tasks in Nim, 
    then add the .nim files in the same folders as your calling source R file and it will 
    compile and load the library into R memory. Depends on nim, nimble and rnim installed in
    your system.
License: MIT
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
